# project-merge

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `projection_pushdown_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (project ?cols1 (project ?cols2 ?input))
rhs: (project ?cols1 ?input)
